title: Men and Boys volume 1 number 1 - Vintage 8mm Porn Promotion Maga
description:
A high-definition scan of a "gay" pornographic magazine I purchased
(for U.S. $5, as you see on the cover!) in 1972, "MEN AND BOYS."

48 pages, scanned as 300 dpi, descreened, and saved in PNG format.
2503 x 3209  Pixels, 8 pages in 24-bit color, and 40 pages in 8-bit grayscale.
 
Like many male/male stroke magazines of its time, this was an advertisement
for two 200-foot regular 8mm color movies by "Sunshine Beach Club," in this
case, the two movies entitled "Hot Water" and "The Coach Scores."

Posted for archival purposes; no color correction or image enhancement has
been performed.
